<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich N., Abt zu Kloster Saalfeld</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Elsbeth und Heinz Kammermeister, Bürger zu Nürnberg, dass ihr vom Kloster Saalfeld zu Lehen gehender Hof zu Dörfles nicht von Heinrich und Günther von Rosenau, Münzmeister von Coburg, mit einem Zehnten für das Kloster Veilsdorf belegt wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_45" id="21v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l24"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Abbt des Cloſters </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l25">cʒu Salfelt ſant Benedicten ordens </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l26"><expan>Erwidıg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Heincʒ Camermeiſter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l27"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd frawn Elſpeten der <expan>Cam<ex>m</ex>ermeiſterin<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l28"> <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> muter 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd ſeinen </del> vnd <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> geſwiſtreid wegen . vvie Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l29"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd Günther die Müncʒmeiſter von <expan>kob<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> . einfell <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l30">in Jren hof cʒum dörffleins . den ſie von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ervvirdikeit vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l31">Stifft <expan>cʒuleh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> als die des ewr brief vnd vrkund <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l32">dy <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> . <expan>Muncʒmeiſte<ex>r</ex></expan> cʒehendhaft <expan>cʒemach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> meinen Alſo . daʒ derſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l33">cʒehend von der ~ <expan>Abtiſſin<ex>n</ex></expan> von Veyelſtorff <expan>cʒuleh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> rüren ſülle . derſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l34">hof mit <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>cʒugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> . doch dy <expan>vorgen<ex>amte</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burgerin<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>Jre<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l35">vater <expan>ſelige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>anerſtorb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd an der <expan>teẏlu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> angefallen ſeẏ . den Jr <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l36">lenger <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> xl Jar vnd ſie ſelber <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> wol bey xiiij Jaren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l37">vncʒehendhaft gehabt vnd herbraht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in ſtiller 
<del rend="strikethrough"> nücʒ </del> nücʒlicher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_45_r1l38">gewere Hyrümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr euch dy <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> vnd Jre kinden </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_46" id="22r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_46_r1l2">darynne vvöllet <expan>günſtiklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen Alſo daʒ ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_46_r1l3">bey <expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jrem hof / als ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> . den von euch vnd <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> Stifft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_46_r1l4"><expan>cʒuleh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd herbraht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gerülich behalten werden daran Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_46_r1l5">vns beſunder gunſt vnd guten willen bevveıſet . das vvir vmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_46_r1l6">ewch vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> Stifft gern verdıenen wöllen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_46_r1l8">Oſwaldi Anno xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_45" id="21v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, abbt des closters czu Salfelt, sant
                        Benedicten ordens</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwidig<ex>er</ex></expan> und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                        uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Heincz Camermeister,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> und frawn
                        Elspeten der <expan>Cam<ex>m</ex>ermeisterin<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> muter, und
                            <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> geswistreid wegen, wie in
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und Günther die Münczmeister von
                                <expan>Kob<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> einfell
                            <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in iren hof czum Dörffleins, den sie von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erwirdikeit und
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> stifft <expan>czu leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        als die des ewr brief und urkund <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hof dy
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Munczmeiste<ex>r</ex></expan> czehendhaft <expan>cze
                            mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> meinen, also daz derselb czehend von der
                                <expan>abtissin<ex>n</ex></expan> von Veyelstorff <expan>czu
                                leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> rüren sülle, derselb hof mit
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>czugehöru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> doch dy
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burgerin<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> vater
                                <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>anerstorb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und an der
                            <expan>teylu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> angefallen sey, den ir
                                <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> lenger <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        xl jar und sie selber <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> wol bey xiiii jaren
                        unczehendhaft gehabt und herbraht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in stiller
                        nüczlicher gewere. Hyrümb <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir euch dy
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> und ire kinden <pb facs="#facs_46" id="22r"/>darynne
                        wöllet <expan>günstiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen, also daz sie bey
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> irem hof, als sie
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> den von euch und
                            <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> stifft <expan>czu leh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und herbraht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, gerülich behalten werden. Daran
                        ir uns besunder gunst und guten willen beweiset, das wir umb ewch und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> stifft gern verdienen wöllen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Oswaldi anno xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
